.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, chinese, british, french, japanese, turkish, brazilian
7 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, bird, chinchilla, dog, horse, cat
 1. the japanese is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 3. the owner of the dog is the brazilian##1
 4. the british is on the left of the turkish##1
 5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 6. the french is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the indonesian is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 8. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the cat and the french##2
 9. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the chinese is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | japanese | indonesian | chinese   | french | british | turkish |
| Pet           | dog | horse     | guinea-pig     | bird | chinchilla   | frog   | cat    |

