.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, almond-milk, cola, soy-milk, 7up, coffee
There are 7 different nationalities: german, american, italian, brazilian, indian, spanish, colombian
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the italian##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the indian##1
 3. the spanish is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the indian##1
 5. the german is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the brazilian is between the person drinking almond-milk and the spanish##2
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
 8. the brazilian is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is the american##1
10. the german is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | soy-milk  | cola  | hot-chocolate  | coffee      | 7up       | mirinda |
| Nationality   | indian | brazilian | spanish | colombian | german | italian | american  |

