.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, d&b, trance, gospel, techno, country, funk
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, boat, trike, airplane, tram, car, subway
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the tram is the fan of d&b##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the fan of funk and the fan of hip-hop##2
4. the fan of country is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the car is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
8. the person driving the boat is the fan of gospel##1
9. the fan of techno is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel      | techno | hip-hop | trance | funk      | d&b      | country |
| Transport     | boat | car | subway       | jet-ski | trike | tram | airplane |

