.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  teacher, lawyer, chef, photographer, nurse, architect, designer
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: ice-hockey, golf, baseball, weightlifting, soccer, surfing, skateboarding
1. the chef is on the left of the designer##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the nurse##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the architect is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is soccer and the teacher##2
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
8. the architect is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | nurse | teacher | photographer | architect | lawyer | chef     | designer |
| Sport   | baseball   | weightlifting    | skateboarding    | soccer      | golf  | ice-hockey | surfing |

