.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, almond-milk, 7up, tea, water, juice
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, climbing, weightlifting, soccer, snowboarding, skiing, sailing
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is the person drinking tea##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is sailing##2
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person drinking tea##2
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | mirinda    | 7up | almond-milk   | water | juice    | tea |
| Sport      | soccer | water-polo | sailing    | climbing | snowboarding    | weightlifting | skiing  |

