.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, 7up, iced-tea, milk, coffee, sprite
The people have 7 different jobs:  scientist, pilot, project-manager, engineer, bartender, musician, videographer
 1. the bartender is on the left of the engineer##1
 2. the scientist is on the left of the project-manager##1
 3. the musician is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the bartender is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking sprite##2
 7. the pilot is on the right of the musician##1
 8. the scientist is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking soy-milk##2
11. the bartender is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | 7up  | milk   | soy-milk         | tea     | sprite              | coffee    | iced-tea     |
| Job        | musician | pilot | bartender | engineer | videographer | scientist | project-manager |

