.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: musical, crime, superhero, epic, comedy, sports, western
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, ship, airplane, roller, train, subway, bike
1. the person watching musical movies is the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the train##2
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the train##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
9. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | epic     | sports | comedy | superhero | western  | musical |
| Transport     | airplane | roller | train   | car     | bike    | ship | subway   |

