.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, water, lemonade, soy-milk, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
The people have 7 different hobbies: rock-climbing, reading, dancing, fishing, drawing, card-games, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
9. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | juice       | hot-chocolate         | soy-milk         | lemonade   | water        | iced-tea |
| Hobby      | collecting | dancing | rock-climbing | drawing | reading | card-games | fishing  |

