7. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

