.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: animation, superhero, disaster, romance, sports, satire, crime
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: metal, electronic, trance, funk, hip-hop, jazz, ambient
 1. the person watching animation movies is the fan of ambient##1
 2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 3. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching romance movies and the fan of metal##2
 4. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching sports movies##2
 5. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
10. the fan of funk is the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
