 3. the person drinking coffee is between the fan of metal and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 4. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 5. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 7. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the fan of blues is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
| Beverage      | juice   | soy-milk | water | coffee | hot-chocolate | cola   | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | blues | gospel | metal     | pop | punk  | dubstep | funk     |

