 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 6. the person eating nectarine is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating pomegranate##1
 8. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking 7up and the person eating nectarine##2
10. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
