 3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person eating peas##2
 5. the person eating pumpkin is the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person eating artichoke is the person drinking cola##1
 8. the person eating cranberry is the person eating cranberry##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | coffee       | juice | tea      | cola | almond-milk       | 7up | sprite |
| Food       | zucchini | cranberry    | cabbage | artichoke    | kiwi | pumpkin   | peas |

