6. the firefighter is on the left of the person eating potato##1
7. the scientist is on the right of the social-worker##1
8. the entrepreneur is between the person eating pear and the firefighter##2
9. the person eating pear is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |         5          |        6        |     7      |
| Food   | plum | kale    | apple | pear | avocado              | kiwi      | potato    |
| Job    | designer | nurse | social-worker  | scientist   | entrepreneur | firefighter | writer |

 